<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-6">Navigation</h1>

<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
  The TUI displays your agents and their PTY sessions. Navigate between them using keyboard shortcuts or the menu.
</p>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">Agents</h2>
<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
  Switch between agents with <code class="text-zinc-300 bg-zinc-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">Ctrl+J</code>
  (next) and <code class="text-zinc-300 bg-zinc-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">Ctrl+K</code> (previous).
  Each agent runs in its own isolated worktree.
</p>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">PTY sessions</h2>
<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
  Each agent can have multiple PTY sessions (e.g., an agent session and a dev server).
  Toggle between them with <code class="text-zinc-300 bg-zinc-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">Ctrl+]</code>.
</p>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">Menu</h2>
<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
  Press <code class="text-zinc-300 bg-zinc-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">Ctrl+P</code> to open the
  command menu. From here you can create agents, manage worktrees, and access other commands.
</p>
